# Authentication System — Implementation Plan (Final)

Admin login/logout using JWT cookies, protecting the `/dashboard` route group.

## Key Compatibility Notes

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Next.js 16**: Uses [proxy.ts](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/proxy.ts) instead of [middleware.ts](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/middleware.ts) — function export renamed to [proxy()](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/proxy.ts#4-31).

> [!WARNING]
> **Prisma 7 + Turbopack**: Must use `prisma-client-js` generator (not `prisma-client`). Import from `@/lib/generated/prisma` (not `/client`).

> [!CAUTION]
> **No `bun --bun`**: The `--bun` flag breaks Turbopack's `node:crypto` resolution. Use `next dev` directly.

---

## Project Structure Conventions

| Concern | Location |
|---------|----------|
| Pages & layouts | `app/` |
| Server actions | `actions/` |
| Components | `components/<feature>/` |
| Utilities & DB | `lib/` |

