## Implemented Changes

### Auth Utilities

#### [NEW] [auth.ts](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/lib/auth.ts)
JWT helpers: [signToken](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/lib/auth.ts#12-19), [verifyToken](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/lib/auth.ts#20-30), [getSession](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/lib/auth.ts#31-37) — uses `jose` + `JWT_SECRET` env var.

---

### Server Actions

#### [NEW] [auth.ts](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/actions/auth.ts)
- [loginAction(prevState, formData)](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/actions/auth.ts#9-48) — validates credentials via bcrypt, sets httpOnly JWT cookie, redirects to `/dashboard`
- [logoutAction()](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/actions/auth.ts#49-54) — deletes cookie, redirects to `/login`

---

### Route Protection

#### [NEW] [proxy.ts](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/proxy.ts)
Next.js 16 proxy convention. Matcher: `["/dashboard/:path*", "/login"]`
- `/dashboard/*` → redirect to `/login` if unauthenticated
- `/login` → redirect to `/dashboard` if already authenticated

---

### Components

#### [NEW] [login-form.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/components/auth/login-form.tsx)
Client component using `useActionState` with [loginAction](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/actions/auth.ts#9-48).

#### [NEW] [logout-button.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/components/auth/logout-button.tsx)
Reusable logout button wrapping [logoutAction](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/actions/auth.ts#49-54).

#### [NEW] [sidebar.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/components/dashboard/sidebar.tsx)
Collapsible sidebar with nav items + integrated logout (user-styled).

